      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for someone who isn't afraid to roll up their sleeves! While it definitely shows its age with significant cosmetic wear and will require mechanical attention to get it back to its best, it's a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer looking for a fixer-upper with potential.",
