    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, some minor door dings, and the clear coat is starting to thin on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some aesthetic imperfections and routine maintenance.",
