    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical vitals are robust, with the critical Vanos system serviced and rod bearings addressed for long-term reliability. The chassis remains flat through corners thanks to a limited-slip differential and reinforced subframe mounting points. While the exterior shows honest age-appropriate wear, the powertrain and drivetrain synchronization are dialed in. Riding on staggered alloys with a firm suspension profile, this M3 offers the raw, analog feedback that defines the era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
